Services

BornOn

http://linksys.com/jnap/bornon/BornOn
This service provides access to device Born-On settings and information stored in the router's internal state.

Service Actions

  • GetBornOnSetupStatus
  • GetBornOnStatus

Actions

GetBornOnSetupStatus

http://linksys.com/jnap/bornon/GetBornOnSetupStatus
This action gets the status of the Born-On setup process in the router.

Note:

This action is safe to call within the context of a transaction.

Input Parameters

This action does not have any input parameters.

Output Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
bornOnSetupStatus ProcessStatus no The state of the Born-On setup process in the router.

Result

http://linksys.com/jnap/bornon/GetBornOnSetupStatusResult
Value Description
OK Success.
Error
_ErrorAbortedAction
_ErrorInvalidInput
_ErrorInvalidOutput
_ErrorNotReady
_ErrorSessionVerification
_ErrorUnauthorized
_ErrorUnexpected
_ErrorUnknownAction
_ErrorUnknownSession

Sample Transaction

POST [request-uri] HTTP/1.1
Host: 192.168.1.1
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in request body]
X-JNAP-Action: "http://linksys.com/jnap/bornon/GetBornOnSetupStatus"

{
}
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in response body]

{
  "result": "OK",
  "output": {
    "bornOnSetupStatus": "Success"
  }
}

GetBornOnStatus

http://linksys.com/jnap/bornon/GetBornOnStatus
This action gets the status of the the factory Born-On process in the router.

Note:

This action is safe to call within the context of a transaction.

Input Parameters

This action does not have any input parameters.

Output Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
bornOnStatus ProcessStatus no The state of the Born-On process in the router.

Enumerations

ProcessStatus

http://linksys.com/jnap/bornon/ProcessStatus
This service provides access to device Born-On settings and information stored in the router's internal state. Values representing the status of a Born-On process.

Enumeration Values

Value Description
Idle The process has not been started.
Running The process is running.
Success The process completed successfully.
Failed The process failed.
